OL,3,CThrill-seeking storm chaser says 'I
OL,4,Ccan't imagine I'll ever be frightened'
OL,6,FStorm chaser Abbi Adair told ITV News
OL,7,FTyne Tees Presenter Amy Lea what
OL,8,Fdrives her passion for extreme weather
OL,10,FA self confessed thrill-seeker with a
OL,11,Fpassion for extreme weather is
OL,12,Fdedicating weeks of her free time to
OL,13,Fchasing storms.
OL,15,FAbbi Adair, from South Shields, told
OL,16,FITV Tyne Tees "I can't imagine I'll
OL,17,Fever be frightened" after spending six
OL,18,Fyears tailing everything from
OL,19,Ftornadoes to thunder and lightening.
