OL,3,CThrill-seeking storm chaser says 'I
OL,4,Ccan't imagine I'll ever be frightened'
OL,6,FThe 50-year-old was inspired by the
OL,7,Ffilm Twister, the loss of her nephew
OL,8,Fand her long-time interest in extreme
OL,9,Fweather.
OL,11,FAbbi said: "As a child, I grew up in
OL,12,FAberdeen, so we were used to really
OL,13,Fheavy snow.
OL,15,F"I've always loved thunder and
OL,16,Flightning, torrential rain, anything
OL,17,Flike that. And I loved Wizard of Oz as
OL,18,Fa child.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
