OL,3,CThrill-seeking storm chaser says 'I
OL,4,Ccan't imagine I'll ever be frightened'
OL,6,F"After watching the first Twister
OL,7,Fmovie, I started to do a bit of
OL,8,Fresearch and realised it wasn't all
OL,9,Funiversity students collecting data
OL,10,Ffor research and found out that you
OL,11,Fcan actually book to go on these tours
OL,12,Fyourself."
OL,14,FAbbi's unusual hobby has seen her
OL,15,Ftravel thousands of miles across the
OL,16,FUnited States. Her last trip, in June,
OL,17,Fwas an 11-day tour covering 4,500
OL,18,Fmiles.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
