OL,3,CThrill-seeking storm chaser says 'I
OL,4,Ccan't imagine I'll ever be frightened'
OL,6,FShe has witnessed hail stones the size
OL,7,Fof golf balls, flash flooding, thunder
OL,8,Fand lightening storms lasting more
OL,9,Fthan eight hours and an "amazing" S-
OL,10,Fbend tornado in Colorado's Prospect
OL,11,FValley.
OL,13,F'They look like gigantic motherships'
OL,15,F"Initially what you're looking at is
OL,16,Fthe sky," continued Abbi. "The skies
OL,17,Fout there just appear bigger because
OL,18,Fyou've got a lot less buildings around
OL,19,Fand you start to see supercells form,
OL,20,Fwhich are the storms which produce the
OL,21,Fthunder and lightning.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
