OL,3,CThrill-seeking storm chaser says 'I
OL,4,Ccan't imagine I'll ever be frightened'
OL,6,FIt is not all fun however, with tours
OL,7,Frequiring journeys of up to ten hours
OL,8,Fspent in a van.
OL,10,FOtherwise, Abbi said the only other
OL,11,Fdownside is the "humidity and
OL,12,Fmosquitoes".
OL,14,FOrganised tours are pricey - costing
OL,15,Fup to about five thousand dollars -
OL,16,Fbut Abbi is addicted and will be
OL,17,Freturning for two back-to-back tours
OL,18,Fin 2026.
